                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="2" writtenLines="43">Only the first and the second chapters of the second section are layed-out into two columns marked in red ink. The formatting of the text reveals that the grammar was composed for a public rather than personal use. In fact, the page layout delimits a writing surface between the right (25 mm), left (20 mm), upper (25 mm), and bottom margins (15 mm).
</layout>
